-1.title: Cardinal George Pell: The Interview
-1.plot: Sky News commentator Andrew Bolt hosts an exclusive one-on-one interview with Roman Catholic Cardinal George Pell live from Rome, Italy, on the recent Royal Commission into Institutional Responses to Child Sexual Abuse. Pell has stated he will not resign over the child abuse allegations and said the Catholic Church was being held unfairly to a higher standard than others institutions.
